Hellplague/ Malice/ Splattercannon:

Hellplague smiled as Malice soon devoured the energon cube he was given.  Once he was finished, he looked around for more.  The Sweep commander chuckled and got off the bed.
&quot;There is more, come and feed.&quot;
She helped him to his feet.  He swayed from side to side a moment, and Hellplague steadied him.  They walked out the doorway and over to Slattercannon, who waited in vehicle mode, laden with energon.  Malice saw it, and transformed into his beast mode.  The skeletal undead T- Rex stalked toward the ship and started chomping down on the cubes.
&quot;Quite an eater, I see,&quot; Splattercannon commented.
Hellplague walked back into the room to get Blacknightmare.
&quot;Come see this.  It&#39;s our pet, demonstrating how he will smash the Maximals!&quot;

